{"tid":1571014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日就！係！社褔界x社工同學集會啦！","createTime":"2019-09-15T09:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T10:28:30.000Z","uid":221244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad6d657d579a4ef8af2c4ae0cc2b2ac8851f0da1","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T09:58:23.000Z","msg":"社福界一直同一眾香港市民同行<br />\n其實一班社工學生都係！！<br />\n面對社會既不公義 <br />\n我地更堅決要捍衛社工既價值<br />\n捍衛心中既價值觀<br />\n守護我地既良知 <br />\n我地要向呢個港共極權表示 <br />\n我地絕對唔會向佢妥協<br />\n我地呢班社工學生縱然面對白色恐怖 都堅決與香港人同行<br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作學生聯會將會喺9月16號1430-1730喺愛丁堡廣場舉辦<br />\n「拒絕噤聲 凝伙結伴」集會 <br />\n（不反對通知書已申請）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家到場支持 聲援一班社工學生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"adf4b6e6cce0eb061e0e524f3b7f0c74b8e26fce","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:24:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"beb0597509962c4778d5092eea4f56cf34eff7bc","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c84791632f89a2cc6bab4409d816c9e7083bbd00","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:26.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5e22809e341e0f147d469ba597364ed788b55293","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4b004ac0cb1a22c7dde6973dbf27fd2c95d5e73a","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3e471edeead4efe98a780f4006b197f3ec11188d","tid":1571014,"uid":139776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"c47c908a3993b529601a755190d11ea8494e9235","tid":1571014,"uid":221244,"like":0,"dislike